data.description: Stunning 1.5 story former Model Home located in Gorgeous Fairfield South. Enjoy stunning views from this open concept floor plan. Be prepared to impress with bamboo wood floors throughout and a one of a kind kitchen, which includes granite countertops, upgraded 42" maple cabinets and a kitchen island. This property boasts additional upgrades such as widened multicolored flagstone/brick stamped concrete driveway, plantation shutters and a beautiful custom built-in entryway bench. Do not miss the opportunity to se this one!
